      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne botan. Garden, ¶ 3 Nov. 1868. ¶ HC: is the date correct? See 68.09.00 where M thanks Joseph for coming to Wilhlem's aid - W is already back in Dresden. See also 68.11.03 where the amount lis...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">68.11.03a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To James Grant</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Q68/17565, unit 750, VPRS 44/P inward registered and unregistered correspondence, VA 538 Department of Crown Lands and Survey, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne botan. Garden,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">3 Nov. 1868.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">HC: is the date correct? See 68.09.00 where M thanks Joseph for coming to Wilhlem's aid - W is already back in Dresden. See also 68.11.03 where the amount listed for publication for 1868 was £150 so that M cannot be suggesting a reduction in this vote<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">for 1869 of £200.</seg>
                     </p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; margin-left: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; color: #C00000; ">See new notes below.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; color: #C00000; ">None of the four letters to JDH in September 1868 mention Wilhelmi, nor any other letter to JDH mentions Wilhelmi.</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; color: #C00000; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>The original<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; color: #C00000; ">1868<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; color: #C00000; ">publications vote was<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; color: #C00000; ">£350, and M proposed £150 for 1869</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In compliance with your instructions I have the honor in pointing out, what reductions might most advantageously be effected in the expenditure of the botanical Garden and the institutions connected therewith during the coming year, as contrasted with the outlay incurred in former years.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <table n="">
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>1, Abolishment of the Office of Assistant<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                           <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                              <p rend="FootnoteText"
                                 style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                                 xml:lang="en">
                                 <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Carl Wilhelmi.</p>
                           </note>
                        </seg>
                     </p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£350<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                           <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                              <p rend="FootnoteText"
                                 style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                                 xml:lang="en">
                                 <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS marginal annotation by Grant, 28 November 1868: 'Appd'.</p>
                           </note>
                        </seg>
                     </p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
            </table>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">This saving for economys sake may well be effected without any injury of the work of the department, in as much as the work hitherto performed by the assistant can be carried out through redistribution of labor by one of the junior employees. In recommending therefore, that the services of the officer alluded to be dispensed with at the end of the year, simply to save the expenditure involved, I beg to solicit, that the full recompensation may be given him, to which under the XVI clause of the Civil Servants Act he becomes entitled. I would further beg leave most respectfully to ask, that in the appointments anew arising by the extension of the Railways or the waterworks or any other Departments you and your honorable Colleagues may be pleased to take the length of time, during which the Assistant was connected with the botanical establishment into most favorable consideration.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #1015FA; ">Wilhelmi left Melbourne in February 1869 and returned to Dresden, where he was elected a member of<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #1015FA; ">Naturwissenschaftlichen gesellschaft Isis in Dresden<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #1015FA; ">at the meeting of 30 September 1869, having with Theodore Müller been a guest at its meeting on 9 September<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont"
                             style="font-style: italic; color: #1015FA; ">(</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont"
                             style="font-style: italic; color: #1015FA; ">Sitzungsberichte und abhandlungen der Naturwissenschaftlichen gesellschaft Isis in Dresden</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #1015FA; ">,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #1015FA; ">Jahr. 1869, pp. 155 and 129 respectively).</seg>
                     </p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <table n="">
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>2, Savings by a slight reduction of the wages and by diminishing to a small extent the number of the employées</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£320</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
            </table>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">By these means all the branches of the active services may be maintained in unimpaired efficiency.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <table n="">
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>3, Reduction of the vote for publishing works on plants by</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£200</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
            </table>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">This reduction will not longer admit of the issue of lithographies, but otherwise the publications can be continued.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <table n="">
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>4, Still farther economizing the forage vote for the carthorses, aviary birds, waterbirds &amp;c</p>
                     <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£80</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>5, Decrease of the vote for stores, building material, fuel, drainpipes, flowerpots &amp;c</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£70</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
            </table>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">This vote cannot possibly be farther reduced as fuel will be required for the constant or frequent working of the engine to raise Yarra water under complete exclusion of the Yan Yean water.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <table n="">
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The total reductions would thus amount to</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£1020<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                           <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn4" n="5">
                              <p rend="FootnoteText"
                                 style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                                 xml:lang="en">
                                 <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #1015FA; ">The amounts given here are<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                                 </seg>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #1015FA; ">comparisons</seg>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #1015FA; ">
                                    <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>with the published estimates for 1868. There had been reductions made during the year, see the estimates in M to J. Grant, 3 November 1868 and notes thereto that record comparisons<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                                 </seg>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #1015FA; ">made by officials<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                                 </seg>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #1015FA; ">between<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                                 </seg>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #1015FA; ">M's 1869 estimates and<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                                 </seg>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #1015FA; ">the</seg>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #1015FA; ">ir</seg>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #1015FA; ">
                                    <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>record<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                                 </seg>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #1015FA; ">for</seg>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #1015FA; ">
                                    <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>1868</seg>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #1015FA; ">. Discrepancies between the officials' 1868 cost</seg>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #1015FA; ">
                                    <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>comparisons<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                                 </seg>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #1015FA; ">
                                    <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                                 </seg>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #1015FA; ">published<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                                 </seg>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #1015FA; ">1868<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                                 </seg>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #1015FA; ">estimate</seg>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #1015FA; ">s are discussed in the notes</seg>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #1015FA; ">.</seg>
                                 <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #1015FA; ">
                                    <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                                 </seg>
                              </p>
                           </note>
                        </seg>
                     </p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
            </table>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">for 1869. The gradual completion of the drive and other heavy work will admit of still farther reductions in 1870.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your obedient servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">The honorable</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">J. M. Grant, M.P. &amp;c &amp;c</p>
         </div>
